    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>此文发布于2020年8月17日。</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><p>衔接上文，宫敏钧购买了流量卡，测试速度。</p><div id="dplayer0" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer0"),"loop":"yes","screenshot":"yes","video":{"url":"http://lc-6lvAVsSD.cn-e1.lcfile.com/05774bf4964264a24c97/F5D87B522435473A63DAB3FD3E4945C8.mp4"},"danmaku":{"api":"https://api.prprpr.me/dplayer/"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script><p>速度比较理想，峰值为每秒441个兆字节（441MB/S）但在使用过程中显示了「数据已停用」弹窗。<br>咨询客服，给出这样的回答： <img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="http://lc-6lvavssd.cn-e1.lcfile.com/5a4af316d86b94e197d0/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200817184150.jpg" alt="image"><br>也就是说，宫敏钧花了37元订购了200G，几乎没用，但后台显示已用60多个G，估计200G也就相当于10G左右！虚假宣传现象是坐实的。<br>客服也并未给宫敏钧退款。</p>]]></content>
    
    
